{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Threat Actor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Threat Actor is a <strong>cybercrime-themed RTS game</strong> featuring a series of campaign maps with increasingly complex mechanics and objectives.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Dark Web</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your criminal enterprise resides on the <strong>Dark Web</strong>, a 3D topdown map filled with various resources, factions and hostile\u00a0<strong>malware entities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete quests, explore the map, create workers to <strong>gather resources</strong> and manage your organization's <strong>income, population and amenity level</strong>. Produce units to defend your base or attack hostile organizations and expand your marketplace by hiring\u00a0<strong>moderators</strong>\u00a0to work for you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About this Demo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Threat Actor demo features the first campaign map which takes around two hours to finish and teaches the player basic game mechanics such as constructing servers, hiring moderators and using your combat units.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2614990?t=1737366936","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2614990?t=1737366936","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614990/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737366936","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614990/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737366936","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Threat Actor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Threat Actor is a <strong>cybercrime-themed RTS game</strong> featuring a series of campaign maps with increasingly complex mechanics and objectives.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Dark Web</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your criminal enterprise resides on the <strong>Dark Web</strong>, a 3D topdown map filled with various resources, factions and hostile\u00a0<strong>malware entities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete quests, explore the map, create workers to <strong>gather resources</strong> and manage your organization's <strong>income, population and amenity level</strong>. Produce units to defend your base or attack hostile organizations and expand your marketplace by hiring\u00a0<strong>moderators</strong>\u00a0to work for you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About this Demo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Threat Actor demo features the first campaign map which takes around two hours to finish and teaches the player basic game mechanics such as constructing servers, hiring moderators and using your combat units.\u00a0</p>","developers":["Nocturne Studio"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2379460","name":"THREAT ACTOR"},"genres":[{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614990/header.jpg?t=1737366936","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257090543,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090543/movie480.mp4?t=1737366930","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090543/movie_max.mp4?t=1737366930"},"name":"DemoTrailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257090543/4a74a1032fccceb1800d93d92ba6ba0c38c59494/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737366930","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090543/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737366930","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090543/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1737366930"}}],"name":"THREAT ACTOR: DEMO","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong